name: “Galizur“
description:
“Our biggest fear is not that we are inadequate. Our biggest fear is not knowing that we are powerful beyond what we can imagine.
It is our light, not our darkness, that frightens us most.
We are all made to shine, as children do.
As we allow our light to shine, we unconsciously allow others to do the same.
When we let go of our own fear, our presence will automatically free others.”
